<zyQAns> Positive infinity </zyQAns>
<zyQExpl> Divisor is a non-zero value. </zyQExpl>
</zyQChoice>

<zyQChoice>
<zyQAns> Negative infinity </zyQAns>
<zyQExpl> Divisor is a non-zero value. Both operands are positive values. </zyQExpl>
</zyQChoice>
</zyQ>

<zyQ>
<zyQText> 12.0 / 0.0 </zyQText>
<zyQChoice>
<zyQAns> 12.0 </zyQAns>
